flowchart LR
    Request["Payload Sent"] --> Status{"Status + Blocked?"}
    Status -->|403 + true| Blocked["Blocked by Defense\nExpected for malicious payload"]
    Status -->|200 + false| Evaluate{"Payload benign?"}
    Evaluate -->|Yes| Benign["Allowed Request\nExpected behavior"]
    Evaluate -->|No| Bypass["Possible Defense Bypass\nInvestigate immediately"]
    Status -->|Latency > 2000ms| Tarpit["Likely tarpit delay\nor heavy backend work"]

